              "bit_width": 1,
              "description": "Allows debug in Stop mode Write access can be protected by PWR_SECCFGR.LPMSEC. The CPU debug and DBGMCU clocks remain active and the HSI16 oscillators is used as system clock during Stop debug mode, allowing CPU debug capability. On exit from Stop mode, the clock settings are set to the Stop mode exit state.",
