              "bit_width": 1,
              "description": "Allows debug in Standby mode Write access can be protected by PWR_SECCFGR.LPMSEC. The CPU debug and DBGMCU clocks remain active and the HSI16 oscillator is used as system clock, the supply and SRAM memory content is maintained during Standby debug mode, allowing CPU debug capability. On exit from Standby mode, a standby reset is performed.",
